 strong for examining status consumption in the developing economies where
 wealth differences are far more conspicuous.
 In thus restating status consumption in the context of wealth differences
 and social stratification, we rely on a social-deference view suggested
 by Corneo 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "corneo_snobbism"
literal "false"

\end_inset

