\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Arguing that status consumption is constituted in this exchange of information
 and risk among the consumers, our objective is to delineate the minimum
 conditions under which status consumption could influence consumer decision.
 To elaborate our notion of security through status goods, we formalise
 the economy of two-consumers who observe an exogenous stochastic wealth
