 with loss-aversion with respect to dynamic reference points (see Lowenstein-Pre
lec 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "LowensteinPrelec1992"
literal "false"

\end_inset

, Brenner et al and Shu et al
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "BrennerVLA2007,ShuPeckOwnership2011"
literal "true"

\end_inset

