 We use a framework of aniticipatory emotions due to Koszegi
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "KoszegiAnticipationPersonalEqlb2010"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 that provides an explicit treatment to dynamic reference points (also see
 Leahy 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "CaplinLeahyAnticipatory2001"
literal "false"

\end_inset

).
 The consumer utility function from prospect theory
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "KahnemanTversykPT1979"
literal "false"

\end_inset

